# Why Callback Tests Passed

Because callback method uses:

```java
HttpServletResponse
```

No session involved.

---

# Better Permanent Fix

Put in `@BeforeEach`

```java id="1aw8b1"
@BeforeEach
void setup() {
    when(request.getSession()).thenReturn(session);
}
```

Then all tests work.

